{
  "stem": "24195.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They didn't call you, really, a half-Jew.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They called you 'Mischling.'",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'Mischling,' which means, really, if you roughly translate it, I would guess it would mean 'of mixed race, mixed origin.'",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[DRINKS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, there were.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were at least two categories.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there might have even-- there might have been even further subsets.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The first category was the category that I was in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was people who had one parent was Jewish and one parent was not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The next category was where only the grandfather, one grandfather, was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they were considered quarter of-- quarters-- a quarter Jewish.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, nobody used that term.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But that-- they were still, like, in a certain sense, a Mischling.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I don't know how far-- how, how much to-- if they-- you know, extended to even more previous generations.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Two, two categories were definitely established.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were-- later on, it was determined that during the Nuremberg War Crime Trials, that the Final Solution of the Nazi-- of the Jewish problem was that, after the extermination of all the people that were, you know, full Jewish, that the next extermination would be the-- of all the people that were half-Jewish.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then possibly the-- that another step would have been the, the people that were a quarter Jewish.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, but they were--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not that I was aware of.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was-- there was not that much of a stigma in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The-- it became a stigma after I went to high school, you know, when I enrolled, and especially after the war had started.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, [SIGHS] it, it turned out that I was the only person-- I mean, I, I, I, I attended school until 1942.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
